Rating: 2
This was ok, but not spectacular. It was very thin in consistency. The day I made this I also made the VANILLA PANNA COTTA WITH MIXED-BERRY COMPOTE from this web site (same type of dish) and I found that the panna cotta was both easier and tastier, so I would not bother making this again.

