Rating: 3
I think this is a bang up "creme" anglaise recipe. I truly love hazelnut so it really appealed to me. And, since it is not a custard or not supposed to be thick, the viscosity was perfect as all "cremes" should be. I will definitely make it again, and also improvise with other liquers using this recipe.

