Rating: 3
I was worried that the consistency was too thin - but if you refrigerate it overnight, it becomes much thicker, but still not as firm as a pudding or mousse. Flavor was good, but couldn't taste much of the Frangelico. I recommend a dallop of fresh whipped cream on top.

Rating: 3
